Parliament, Wednesday 26 June 2019 – The National Council of Provinces held its first ordinary sitting since it was constituted on 23 May to elect its House Chairpersons, Programming Whip and its 11 Select Committee Chairpersons.
	
	The plenary sitting elected Mr Jomo Nyambi as House Chairperson for Committees, Ms Winnie Ngwenya as House Chairperson for Oversight and Institutional Support and Mr Edward Joyisile Njandu as the National Council of Provinces’ Programming Whip.
	
